pageContext.claim: “I wonder if the New York Times will apologize to me a second time, as they did after the 2016 Election. But this one will have to be a far bigger &  better apology. On this one they will have to get down on their knees & beg for forgiveness-they are truly the Enemy of the People!”
pageContext.analysis: The New York Times did not apologize to its subscribers for its coverage of Trump.
